Hello, Quarto

library(data.table)
data = fread('~/Downloads/test_umap_quarto.tsv', header = T)
ojs_define(umap_data = data)
groups = list()
groups$orig.ident = unique(data$orig.ident)
groups$seurat_clusters = unique(data$seurat_clusters)
groups$SingleR.HPC.main = unique(data$SingleR.HPC.main)
ojs_define(groups = groups)
viewof view_var = Inputs.select(new Map([["Sample",'orig.ident'],['Cluster', 'seurat_clusters'],['SingleR','SingleR.HPC.main']]),
{value: "orig.ident", label: "Use coloring Method"})

viewof view_items = Inputs.checkbox(groups[view_var], {label: "Clusters", value: groups[view_var]})

plot_data1 = transpose(umap_data)


filtered1 = plot_data1.filter(function(data){
            return view_items.includes(data[view_var]);
})


Plot.plot({
    grid: true,
    inset: 10,
    marks: [
        Plot.dot(plot_data1, {x: "UMAP_1", y : "UMAP_2", fill : "#ddd", r: 2}),
        Plot.dot(filtered1, {x: "UMAP_1", y: "UMAP_2", fill : view_var})
    ]
})
